title: Ore no Imouto ga Konnani Kawaii Wake ga Nai.
synopsis: Kirino is back from her trip to America, but the fun doesn't stop here! In the second season of Ore no Imouto ga Konnani Kawaii Wake ga Nai , Kyousuke continues to give Kirino life consultations. This time, romance lurks on the horizon for both siblings...
